profile: Mr. Fencee Inc is a Toronto based, Eco-friendly, maintenance-free fence company with over 7 years of experience. Offering clients the best quality fences at unbeatable prices with the fastest installation times in Ontario. We offer fence installations in the regions of GTA, Toronto, Mississauga, Scarborough, Markham, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Newmarket, King City, Bradford, Brampton, Oakville, Oshawa, Bradford etc. Our aim is to provide modern, and innovative fence designs at the lowest prices. Our fences are unique and manufactured domestically in North York using only recycled materials, better for the environment is better for us. There are no wooden products involved in the manufacturing or during installation of Mr. Fencee fences. More importantly, Mr. Fencee Fences are made in Canada, made for Canada, withstanding the most severe weather conditions and up to 147km/hr winds.
warranty_terms: 2 Years Labor and Lifetime Product Warranties

profile:
Have you worked with landscaping contractors before who rush through the job and leave a mess of your yard? Do you now struggle to trust someone to take care of your lawn?

We’re a team of dedicated landscaping professionals who are well-known for getting any landscaping project done right, the first time around. We’re passionate about helping homeowners and business owners reach their landscaping goals and we take pride in our ability to provide high-quality services at an affordable price.
Since opening our doors in 2018, we’ve been able to expand our service areas all thanks to our trusted customers who rely on us as their long-term landscaping partner. If you live in Rockwood, Guelph, or the KW area, give us a call or request a free quote to discuss all your landscaping needs and how we can help you accomplish them.

We offer services such as:
Design
Build
Maintenance
Snow Removal

And more!

Check us out here:

profile:
At London Fab we can do your custom metal fabrication, practically any metal project idea. Check out the portfolio of projects skillfully crafted in metal for our residential, retail, commercial and contractor clients.

Using leading edge 3D modeling software we design custom graphics and precision parts. The CNC plasma parts and fabrications are made locally at our London Ontario location. We can use steel, stainless steel or aluminum, flat sheet and various tubing materials and custom powder coating, just ask us!

High quality, precision, custom, metal fabrication services we provide include: railings, steel railings, outdoor railings, metal hand railings, deck railings, gates, driveway gates, farm gates, man gates, arch gates, security gates, privacy gates, horizontal gates, rolling gates, sliding gates, remote control gates, Automatic/Electric/Rolling/Swing/slide driveway gates, Keyless/Keypad/lock gates, fences, fence panels, porch, pool fence, steel privacy fence, screens, balcony screens, security screens, privacy screens, chain links, metal columns, stairs, spiral stairs, ornamental railings, driveways, brackets, deck brackets, gazebo, gazebo brackets, pool brackets, metal signs, signage, sign graphics, sign frames, pool signs, LED signs, tables, table bases, live edge table bases, ramps, staircases, planters, engine mounts, lift kits, transmission mounts, tractor parts & more. Wrought iron metal, stainless steel, glass, ornamental, modular, decorative, galvanized. Contact us for free estimates.

profile:
At Frontier Fencing and Decks we have 3 simple rules:

We will strive to construct only the highest quality projects and build a lasting product that will continue to please for years to come.

Our business is built around your needs, which is why we take the time to meet with you and work together to ensure 100% satisfaction in design and finished product.

We are always fair and competitive in pricing, and we stand behind our work to instill confidence and trust.

John and Jonathan Jagt of Frontier Fencing and Decks have built a reliable team of professional contractors who will help bring your design ideas to life! 

Unsure of what you want? Let us help! We are well versed in all different types of fences, decks, pergolas, privacy screens....

We can help design and build your dream project, literally, from the ground up.
